comment:
For what I make of him, I think JD is a creep and a drunken beast who has no scruples and no respect for women. 

Amber looked clearly injured as there are marks/bruises all over her face (none on Johnny). And he is known for his heavy drinking and being a wild man, and carried the "bad boy" image for a very long time. Also had a whole catalogue of relationship/marriage breakups (where there is smoke there is usually fire). Also, there is clear video-footage of him whilst in a wild/crazy drunken and aggressive stupor, where he is violently smashing things. Therefore how can anyone doubt what the man is capable of. Of course he would be considered aggressive/dangerous enough to attack someone. Realistically, we are not looking at a "gentleman" or a "saint" here. I myself was trapped in an abusive marriage with a man like that and so I have first-hand experience what damage a man can do whilst he is under the influence of too much alcohol and in that same type of stupor.        

All of the big-name, so called "witnesses" who are taking Johnny's side against Amber - he must've paid them off with an awful lot of money (after all the man is minted to the hilt). And most of those actors/actresses are like very high-class whores who will do "anything" for "money". And no matter how much money they have, it is never "enough" (a case of too much & never enough). And they have no soul either. 

I am not a fan of Johnny Depp - and so I would be seeing him for what he is - not fantasising about what he is not, or looking at him through rose-tinted glasses. I am seeing a caveman who seriously needs to sort his head out, or soon end up on skid row (or much worse).
